items.details: Well done on all your hard work for World Heritage Day! I think we all learned a lot about Ireland and also about the countries we visited. You made me very proud with how well you listened to the teachers and took notes. The homework will carry over from yesterday, so please check yesterday’s homework. The photos will be uploaded to the 3-1 photo site today or tomorrow. Also, thanks for all the delicious food! I am stuffed, and the food reminded me of home! Thanks, and have a great evening!
